name: Studio Visit #1
description:
#Studio Visit with an Artist (Omakase Time)

You joined an intimate session with the pioneering artist, Rejane Cantoni. It was an “omakase” theme because it was all about establishing personal, intimate connections behind the story of artists.

This is a limited edition NFT given to you alongside fellow collectors in the room. The picture on the artwork is a part of Rejane’s project called FLORAS.
